16/10/2000  Using SUNPro cc, the new version of force.c is over 10% faster with
            -xinline= to turn off inlining. Hwever ewald is slower by 20%.
07/12/2000  Compiling on IBM SP2.  Use env CC=mpcc CPPFLAGS=-I/usr/lpp/ppe.poe/include
            This works around a stupid bug which produces a spurious warning message
            on "mpcc -E" which causes the configure to fail.
